Clients


Who We ServeNew Client IntakeCase Studies















			Who We Serve		

At Blume Capital, we serve individuals, families, foundations and retirement plans with $1 million or more of investable assets.
While the backgrounds of our client base are diverse, Blume Capital attracts clients who value experience and professional competence, personal involvement, independent advice, and understand the conflicts inherent in larger financial institutions.
Our clients reside throughout the United States and abroad and include:

Professionals
Entrepreneurs
Retirees
High net worth individuals and families
Business owners
Recipients of inheritances

Blume Capital Management is a fee-only investment advisory firm. We are compensated only by our clients. There are no indirect or hidden fees, and we neither pay nor accept sales fees or commissions of any kind.













